<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FFAF6A10FCEE90971B43BCE1" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFFAF6A10FCEE90971B43BCE1" blockId="84.[785,1378,1616,2042]" pageId="84" pageNumber="842">
Congeners 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FC4290971A50BDD5" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[958,1104,1742,1767]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alienus">H. alienus</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FB9190971B11BDD5" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[1133,1297,1742,1767]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">H. laephotis</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FCEE90B41DE1BC3C" authorityName="R. A. Philippi" authorityYear="1866" box="[786,993,1773,1806]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="940" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="magellanicus">H. magellanicus</taxonomicName>
were previously considered subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FC1C91441A91BC04" authorityName="R. A. Philippi &amp; Landbeck" authorityYear="1861" box="[992,1169,1821,1846]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Vespertilio" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="montanus">H. montanus</taxonomicName>
, and its taxonomic status is confusing. It is frequently mistaken with 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FC21913A1A76BCB6" authorityName="Thomas" authorityYear="1916" box="[989,1142,1891,1924]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="laephotis">H. laephotis</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFFAF6A10FB41913A1B5ABCB6" baseAuthorityName="Poeppig" baseAuthorityYear="1835" box="[1213,1370,1891,1924]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Histiotus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="84" pageNumber="842" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="macrotus">H. macrotus</taxonomicName>
; therefore, accurate data from literature are scarce. Three subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
